longBusinessSummary: Merkur PrivatBank KgaA provides various private banking products and services in Germany. The company offers business and private accounts; fixed deposits; securities accounts; asset management; mastercards; and SME and developer financing, and leasing refinancing services. It also offers online banking services. The company was founded in 1923 and is based in Munich, Germany.
